<gpx version="1.1" creator="Hikingbook" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1 https://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1/gpx.xsd https://hikingbook.net/xmlschemas/1/5 https:/hikingbook.net/xmlschemas/1/5/gpxhb.xsd" xmlns:gpxhb="https://hikingbook.net/xmlschemas/1/5"><metadata><name>🪢太極峽谷-(2025-04-19）-「溪降」［🇹🇼南投-竹山］</name><desc>W-waterfall (瀑布）&#xA;S-slideway (滑瀑）&#xA;L-left(左岸）&#xA;TL-TopLeft(高左岸）&#xA;BL-BottomLeft(低左岸）&#xA;R-right(右岸）&#xA;TR-TopRight(高右岸）&#xA;BR-BottomRight(低右岸）&#xA;C-center(中岸）&#xA;&#xA;WT-waterfalltop(瀑頂）&#xA;WB-waterfallbottom(瀑底）&#xA;M-middle(中繼點）&#xA;D-deep(深潭）&#xA;G-guide (滑降）&#xA;B-bolt(人工錨點）&#xA;N-nature(天然錨點）&#xA;PB-personal bolt (人力錨點）&#xA;DB-damaged bolt(損壞錨點）&#xA;TR-Traverse(橫移）&#xA;&#xA;Ex: &#xA;W1(M1-L)-B2-18m，D-5m&#xA;「瀑布1（中繼點1-左岸）-bolt有兩顆-使用繩長18米，深潭5公尺長」&#xA;&#xA;成員：&#xA;潾兒、Jimce、簡建輝、丹丹、志霖、銘哲&#xA;&#xA;裝備：&#xA;繩- &#xA;台製  9.0-30m&#xA;Humna 8.5-100m&#xA;CE4Y (V2) 9.0-100m&#xA;Humna 8.5-50m&#xA;&#xA;電鑽組*1&#xA;（M8)Bolt*15set&#xA;&#xA;砍刀*1&#xA;&#xA;面鏡*1&#xA;呼吸管*1&#xA;&#xA;急救包：&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;無線電-&#xA;457.51250&#xA;</desc><author><name>Hikingbook</name><link href="https://hikingbook.net"><text>Hikingbook</text></link></author><link href="https://hikingbook.net/hikes/2025-4-19-%E6%99%A8%E9%96%93%E9%87%8D%E8%A3%9D%E7%99%BB%E5%B1%B1-4d4eb2b3"><text>Hikingbook</text></link><time>2026-06-04T17:09:37.484564491+08:00</time><keywords>Hikingbook,EzLife ,太極峽谷,南投,竹山,溪降,canyoning ,Taiwan,台灣,青龍瀑布</keywords><extensions><gpxhb:postscript>4-6🈷️，18-20時間點有螢火蟲

水管路=
明顯路跡+
沿路都有三通管降溫+
拉繩+
一個過濾水塔（裝水）

W6bolt打一個新的在中間石頭正上方…
側邊容易沖毀。


中途有等待隊友2-3小時…
拍照花費1小時，
如果腳程都沒問題，則僅需10小時附近</gpxhb:postscript><gpxhb:loadweight>10.0</gpxhb:loadweight><gpxhb:fitnesslevel>3</gpxhb:fitnesslevel><gpxhb:activitytype>others</gpxhb:activitytype><gpxhb:trackimageurl>https://assets.hikingbook.net/users/60w3wu1it91y2jmwdxciziq/ertntcajqh2dgtcaufn65g/07e6ff61-ab75-4afb-8f44-a6fb7a01ae91.jpg</gpxhb:trackimageurl><gpxhb:device>Apple iPhone 13 Pro</gpxhb:device><gpxhb:source>Hikingbook</gpxhb:source></extensions></metadata><wpt lat="23.658479601166825" lon="120.73657304059782"><ele>725</ele><time>2025-04-18T22:54:56Z</time><name>00 S</name><cmt>2025-04-19T06:54:56+08:00</cmt><desc>00 S</desc><src>Hikingbook</src><link href="https://hikingbook.net/hikes/ERtNtCAJQH2dgTcAuFn65g"><text>Hikingbook</text></link><extensions><gpxhb:weather>Clear</gpxhb:weather><gpxhb:speed>0.230000</gpxhb:speed><gpxhb:course>211.640625</gpxhb:course></extensions></wpt><wpt lat="23.660203307050033" lon="120.73577365400705"><ele>642</ele><time>2025-04-18T23:05:50Z</time><name>01 玉福吊橋</name><cmt>2025-04-19T07:05:50+08:00</cmt><desc>01 玉福吊橋</desc><src>Hikingbook</src><link href="https://hikingbook.net/hikes/ERtNtCAJQH2dgTcAuFn65g"><text>Hikingbook</text></link><extensions><gpxhb:weather>Clear</gpxhb:weather><gpxhb:speed>0.491701</gpxhb:speed><gpxhb:course>27.817940</gpxhb:course></extensions></wpt><wpt lat="23.66109995173631" lon="120.73578631516614"><ele>645</ele><time>2025-04-18T23:23:48Z</time><name>02 W1(WT-L-B1-5m)（太極峽谷）</name><cmt>2025-04-19T07:23:48+08:00</cmt><desc>02 W1(WT-L-B1-5m)（太極峽谷）</desc><src>Hikingbook</src><link href="https://hikingbook.net/hikes/ERtNtCAJQH2dgTcAuFn65g"><text>Hikingbook</text></link><extensions><gpxhb:weather>Clear</gpxhb:weather><gpxhb:speed>0.000000</gpxhb:speed><gpxhb:course>-1.000000</gpxhb:course></extensions></wpt><wpt lat="23.66114232225037" lon="120.73567567404429"><ele>638</ele><time>2025-04-19T00:06:08Z</time><name>03 W1(M1-L-B2-58m，D-20m) （太極峽谷）</name><cmt>2025-04-19T08:06:08+08:00</cmt><desc>03 W1(M1-L-B2-58m，D-20m) （太極峽谷）</desc><sr